data.description: SELLER TO PAY UP TO $5,000 TOWARDS BUYERS CLOSING COSTS AND OR PREPAIDS!! Motivated seller, make your appointment for a viewing today and check out the video!! If you are looking for a house that is beautifully maintained with modern updates, over 2200 sq ft of finished living space, in a wonderful neighborhood, and fantastic school district then this is your dream home!! Tucked away in Driftwood Subdivision and in the cul-de-sac is this special 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom family home, with ample space to grow! Entering the living room off the front porch you will immediately be impressed with the abundance of light filtering through the whole house. This home features bay windows, hardwood flooring throughout, stone fireplace with gas, an oversized family room (approx 30x24) with vaulted ceilings, and a kitchen with updated appliances. Just a couple of steps away is the primary bedroom with a cute, updated half bath. There are 2 additional bedrooms along with a full bathroom with new tile and vanity. Moving downstairs you will find a finished space currently being used as a bedroom/playroom. Also, downstairs there is a laundry room, flex space, and workshop area with walkout access. If you like spending time outdoors, you will love this backyard with its beautiful covered back deck and level seating area for entertaining. There is also a large yard barn for storage that conveys with the house along with the front load washer & dryer and 2022 Whirlpool refrigerator.
